&lt;p&gt;Output metrics in InfluxDB line protocol&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="synopsis"&gt;Synopsis&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Output device metrics in InfluxDB line protocol format.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outputs power, voltage, current, and energy metrics from all registered
devices (or a specified subset) in InfluxDB line protocol format suitable
for piping to InfluxDB or Telegraf.&lt;/p&gt;
